A' chaid chlar le [[Dr. Dre]], a bha na bhall de [[N.W.A.]] roimhe sin.  Thainig e a-mach ann an 1992 agus bha e ainmeil airson nan oran,[[Ain't Nuthin Like a G-Thang]], [[Fuck wit' Dre Day (And Everybody Celebrating)]] and [[Let Me Ride]].

Tha 'Chronic' na sheorsa de [[Canaib|Chanaib]] gu math laidir le corr is 50 ceudnad dheth mar [[THC]], tha e gu math pailt a-measg nan duine dubha ann am Baile nan Aingeal.  Bidh [[Cypress Hill] a' toirt iomradh air 'Chronich' air an claran cuideachd.
